## ğŸ’¾ Save System

The game utilizes **Local Storage** to automatically save your data. Your progress remains safe between sessions as long as you do not clear your browser's cache.

**Stored Data includes:**
* Highest level reached & Achievements.
* Story progression & total coins collected.
* Personal leaderboard statistics.

